METAL PACKAGES INDUSTRIES
TECHNICAL DATA SHEET: PHARMACEUTICAL ALUMINIUM COLLAPSIBLE TUBES

1. PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
Premium quality flexible aluminium collapsible tubes manufactured under strict GMP compliance, specifically engineered for pharmaceutical ointments, creams, gels, and eye drops.

2. SPECIFICATIONS & DIMENSIONS
- Diameter Range: 13.5 mm to 30.0 mm
- Wall Thickness: 0.10 mm - 0.15 mm
- Capacity: 5 ml to 30 ml
- Purity: 99.7% pure refined aluminium slugs
- Thread Type: Standard DIN threads (DIN 13 / DIN 168)

3. COATINGS & FINISHES
- Internal Lacquer: Double-coated Epoxy-phenolic resin (fully cured, food & drug grade)
- Base Coat: Titanium dioxide white base coat
- External Print: High-resolution offset printing up to 6 colors
- Latex Lining: High-viscosity food-grade end-band latexing for absolute seal integrity

4. APPLICATIONS
- Sterile Ointments
- Antiseptic Creams
- Ophthalmic Gels
- Topical Medications

5. CERTIFICATIONS
- ISO 9001:2015 Certified
- GMP Compliant Manufacturing
- FDA Compliant raw materials

